rbucks，利用咖啡店的電源去挖礦。由於她以 Starbucks 偷電去節省電費成本，她以該筆電的效能，再配合當日以太幣的價格，結果計算出每日收入大概 23 人民幣（折合 HK$27.6）左右。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/nb/img/2021-02/12/27742/eprice_8_09f867aeaa3aac219f903bb3cba9427a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fnb%2Fimg%2F2021-02%2F12%2F27742%2Feprice_8_09f867aeaa3aac219f903bb3cba9427a.jpg&h=7d343ea7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這位網紅在 Starbucks 呆坐了 4 小時，結果從挖礦而來的收入為 4.5 人民幣（約 HK$5.4），她不但教網民在 Starbucks 偷電，更想出 24 小時挖礦的絕招，就是早上到 Starbucks，晚上則去 24 小時營業的麥當勞繼續，她表示這樣才不易被人發現。她又表示以每天收入 23 人民幣計算，約 260 天就可以將價值約 6,000 人民幣的筆電回本，假如啟動超頻模式，更可以將時間縮短約 30 多天"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T20:02:41.000Z","msg":"手提電腦都拎黎mine coins <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbcb9f7b41ffbd1afb28aefd9add59a53a4665f","tid":2405110,"uid":33874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e54e1c7edf417eecfa628d1f7fdba33b515f362","tid":2405110,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"37cca6d5cac4f9be667d85072ee40b82ee6481f9","tid":2405110,"uid":206827,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"quote":{"pid":"d7444ef726e67222a0e342fac3ce718372799cc1","tid":2405110,"uid":109573,"like":461,"dislike":0,"score":461,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:28:52.000Z","msg":"鳩坐一日得幾蚊，何必"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T14:09:09.000Z","msg":"點同 大陸人時間同命都唔值錢 果幾蚊應該夠三餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T18:14:57.000Z","msg":"唔好咁冇腦好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢手上面杯嘢飲等於佢挖一個禮拜喇，人地做吓實驗，你就當正人地真係靠哩個開飯。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T20:10:08.000Z","msg":"總之支那雞就要笑鳩佢啦"},{"pid":"99e3f993335518f7c8cb4040bf562cf21610708b","tid":2405110,"uid":245484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T20:11:18.000Z","msg":"咖啡都未撚夠買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\